<title>USA: NutraMax completes repurchase of stock from MEDIQ.</title>
<headline>NutraMax completes repurchase of stock from MEDIQ.</headline>
<dateline>GLOUCESTER, Mass 1996-12-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>NutraMax Products Inc, a manufacturer and marketer of health and personal care products, said Tuesday it had completed the $36.3 million repurchase of 47 percent of its outstanding shares of common stock from MEDIQ Inc.</p>
<p>The company said it had paid MEDIQ $19.9 million in cash and given it a promissory note for the remaining $16.4 million.</p>
<p>Each share was worth $9.00, it added.</p>
